tton\" class=\"submit\" value=\"Post to Evernote\"/>\\n<a href=\"javascript:void(0);\" class=\"cancel_box\">cancel</a>\\n</div>\\n</form>\\n</div>\\n</div>\\n</div>\\n<!-- Article Title / Metadata overlay that shows up on scroll -->\\n<aside id=\"left_context_metadata\" class=\"js_control_bar_recall left_context_metadata\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\\n<div class=\"metadata\">\\n<header>Airbus Soars Past Boeing by Showing Little Mercy to Struggling Customers - WSJ</header>\\n\\n<div class=\"source\">\\n<div class=\"site_name\">\\n<a class=\"original\" href=\"https://www.wsj.com/articles/airbus-boeing-rivals-max-11626189853\">wsj.com</a>\\n</div>\\n\\n<div class=\"site_domain\">\\n<a class=\"original\" href=\"https://www.wsj.com/articles/airbus-boeing-rivals-max-11626189853\">WSJ</a>\\n</div>\\n\\n</div>\\n\\n\\n<time class=\"meta_read_time\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\\n0 min\\n</time>\\n\\n</div>\\n\\n</aside>\\n</section>\\n<section id=\"swap_logo_capital\" class=\"js_control_bar_recall swap_logo_capital\">\\n<aside class=\"logo_capital\"></aside>\\n</section>\\n<section id=\"recall_indicator\" class=\"recall_indicator\">\\n<a href=\"javascript:void(0);\" class=\"js_control_bar_recall\">\\n<span class=\"ipicon ipicon-ellipsis\"></span>\\n</a>\\n</section>\\n</nav>\\n\\n</div>\\n</div>\\n<div class=\"container read_content_container\">\\n<main class=\"main\" aria-label=\"Article\">\\n\\n\\n<div class=\"badge-container read-tag-container js_read_tag_container\"></div>\\n\\n<div id=\"titlebar\" class=\"titlebar\">\\n<h1>Airbus Soars Past Boeing by Showing Little Mercy to Struggling Customers - WSJ</h1>\\n<span class=\"origin_line\">\\n\\n<a class=\"original\" href=\"https://www.wsj.com/articles/airbus-boeing-rivals-max-11626189853\">WSJ</a>\\n\\n&middot;\\n\\nby <span class=\"author\">Benjamin Katz</span>\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n</span>\\n\\n</div>\\n<div id=\"story\"data-id=\"1428152861\" data-words=\"76\" class=\"story\">\\n<section><p>Last summer, while his airline was burning through more than $1.2 million an hour, <span><a href=\"https://www.wsj.com/market-data/quotes/XE/XETR/LHA\">Deutsche Lufthansa</a></span> AG Chief Executive Carsten Spohr signed onto a video call to meet his counterpart at <span><a href=\"https://www.wsj.com/market-data/quotes/FR/XPAR/AIR\">Airbus SE</a> <a href=\"https://www.wsj.com/market-data/quotes/FR/XPAR/AIR\">AIR <span>1.43%</span><span><span>increase; green up pointing triangle</span></span></a></span>, the world\\xe2\\x80\\x99s biggest plane manufacturer.</p><p>At the top of Mr. Spohr\\xe2\\x80\\x99s agenda, according to people familiar with the conversation: He wanted a respite from the billions Lufthansa owed for aircraft it had ordered years before the pandemic.</p></section>\\n</div>\\n<footer id=\"footer\" class=\"footer\">\\n<span class=\"origin_line\">\\n\\n<a class=\"original\" href=\"https://www.wsj.com/articles/airbus-boeing-rivals-max-11626189853\">WSJ</a>\\n\\n&middot;\\n\\nby <span class=\"author\">Benjamin Katz</span>\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n</span>\\n</footer>\\n<!-- ### Parser\\nInstaparser\\n-->\\n</main>\\n</div>\\n<!-- Modals -->\\n<div id=\"modal_backer\" class=\"modal_backer\"></div>\\n\\n\\n<div id=\\'speedTimeRemaining\\' class=\\'speed_time_remaining container read_content_container speed_controls_ui\\'></div>\\n<div id=\\'speedRead\\' class=\\'landing_constrained container-fluid size2mode speed_read\\' data-timeSaved=\"None\"  data-remaining=\"10\"  style=\\'display:none\\'>\\n<div id=\\'speedReadProgress\\' class=\\'progress_bar speed_controls_ui\\' style=\\'top:-70px\\'></div>\\n<div id=\\'speedWordContainer\\' class=\\'single-word speed_playmode_ui visible\\'>&nbsp;</div>\\n<div id=\\'speedScrollerContainer\\' class=\\'scroller-wrapper speed_controls_ui\\' >\\n<div id=\\'speedScroller\\' class=\\'scroller\\'>\\n\\n<span id=\"speedWord-0\">Last&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-1\">summer,&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-2\">while&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-3\">his&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-4\">airline&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-5\">was&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-6\">burning&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-7\">through&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-8\">more&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-9\">than&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-10\">$1.2&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-11\">million&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-12\">an&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-13\">hour,&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-14\">Deutsche&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-15\">Lufthansa&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-16\">AG&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-17\">Chief&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-18\">Executive&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-19\">Carsten&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-20\">Spohr&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-21\">signed&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-22\">onto&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-23\">a&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-24\">video&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-25\">call&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-26\">to&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-27\">meet&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-28\">his&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-29\">counterpart&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-30\">at&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-31\">Airbus&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-32\">SE&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-33\">AIR&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-34\">1.43%&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-35\">increase;&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-36\">green&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-37\">up&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-38\">pointing&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-39\">triangle&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-40\">,&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-41\">the&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-42\">world\\xe2\\x80\\x99s&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-43\">biggest&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-44\">plane&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-45\">manufacturer.&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-46\">At&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-47\">the&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-48\">top&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-49\">of&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-50\">Mr.&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-51\">Spohr\\xe2\\x80\\x99s&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-52\">agenda,&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-53\">according&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-54\">to&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-55\">people&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-56\">familiar&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-57\">with&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-58\">the&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-59\">conversation:&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-60\">He&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-61\">wanted&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-62\">a&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-63\">respite&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-64\">from&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-65\">the&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-66\">billions&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-67\">Lufthansa&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-68\">owed&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-69\">for&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-70\">aircraft&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-71\">it&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-72\">had&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-73\">ordered&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-74\">years&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-75\">before&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-76\">the&nbsp;</span><span id=\"speedWord-77\">pandemic.&nbsp;</span>\\n<span id=\"speedWord-78\">\\xe2\\x97\\x86</span>\\n\\n</div>\\n<div id=\\'speedFadeoutLeft\\' class=\\'fade_left\\'></div>\\n<div class=\\'fade_right\\'></div>\\n</div>\\n<div id=\\'speedRuler\\' style=\"visibility: hidden\" class=\\'scroller\\'>\\n\\nLast summer, while his airline was burning through more than $1.2 million an hour, Deutsche Lufthansa AG Chief Executive Carsten Spohr signed onto a video call to meet his counterpart at Airbus SE AIR 1.43% increase; green up pointing triangle , the world\\xe2\\x80\\x99s biggest plane manufacturer. At the top of Mr. Spohr\\xe2\\x80\\x99s agenda, according to people familiar with the conversation: He wanted a respite from the billions Lufthansa owed for aircraft i